🌍 Static Tourism Website
A simple static website built using HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap 4 to showcase popular tourist destinations in India. This project is focused on UI design using only front-end technologies—no JavaScript used.

✨ Features
📌 Multiple tourist spots like Taj Mahal, Golden Temple, Mysore Palace, and Varanasi Temple

🖼️ Image carousels using Bootstrap components

🎨 Clean and organized layout with custom styling and Google Fonts

🗂️ Section-based navigation using Bootstrap classes

🔗 Lightweight and easy to deploy as a static site

📁 Tech Stack
HTML5

CSS3

Bootstrap 4

Google Fonts
